# Testing

Mirror `src/` under `test/` (see `test/README.md`). Run: `bun test`.

**Do not shape production code for tests** — no `deps` optional params, no `@test-export` markers.

| Layer | Approach |
|-------|----------|
| Pure helpers (`event-equality`, `diffTimetables`, `YearWeek`, `to*Dto`) | Import directly, assert |
| Services | `mock.module` repos/caches/senders; test public exports |
| Repositories | `createDb(':memory:')` + migrations; mock `getDb` if needed |
| Private helpers | Test via public caller, or export only if tests would be unreadable otherwise |

**Good first tests** (from refactor plan): `refresh-timetables.service.test.ts`, `event-equality.test.ts`, `year-week.test.ts`, request mappers.

**Caches in tests:** `createCache()` for isolated instances, or `mock.module` the feature cache helper. Never persist timetable data to disk in tests.
